---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HorizontalCard from "../components/HorizontalCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Patents | Ha Cam Thanh LE" sideBarActiveItemID="patents">
  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">Intellectual Property & Patents</div>
  </div>

  <div class="mb-10 text-justify">
    My work at the intersection of <b>Applied Mathematics</b> and <b>Embedded AI</b> has resulted in several technological breakthroughs. Currently, I am the author of 6 research patents focusing on Ultra-Wideband (UWB) systems, signal processing, and secure localization.
  </div>

  <div class="mb-5">
    <div class="text-2xl w-full font-bold">Featured Inventions</div>
  </div>

  
  
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>
  <HorizontalCard
    title="	System and methods for Compression and Decompression of Ultra Wideband Radar Chanel Impulse Responses"
    img="/patent_rtls.webp"
    desc="Efficient method for Data Compression for UWB Radar Signals to be transmitted to the central ECU"
    url="#"
    badge="Pending: Application No. US63969831 (Qorvo Inc)"
  />

  <HorizontalCard
    title="	System and methods for determining Users' Intent in Access Applications"
    img="/patent_rtls.webp"
    desc="Advanced user’s intent detection for more realistic scenarios"
    url="#"
    badge="Pending: Application No. US63878716 (Qorvo Inc)"
  />

  <HorizontalCard
    title="	System for Resolving directional ambiguity in Radio Frequenct Door Lock Applications"
    img="/patent_rtls.webp"
    desc="A system-level solution going with a determinist algorithm for solving the directional ambiguity in Access Control"
    url="#"
    badge="Pending: Application No. PCT/US2026/017633 (Qorvo Inc)"
  />

  <HorizontalCard
    title="	System and methods for determining Users' Intent in Access Applications"
    img="/patent_rtls.webp"
    desc="AI algorithm for user’s intent detection for Access Control Applications"
    url="#"
    badge="Pending: Application No. US19401033 (Qorvo Inc)"
  />

  <div class="divider my-0"></div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="System and methods for untracked navigation using optimized localization algorithm"
    img="/patent_auto.webp"
    desc="A patented method for RTLS using UWB Time Difference of Arrivals (TDOA), ensuring low-latency response and high robust localization."
    url="#"
    badge="Publication No. WO2025240055A1"
  />

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Systems and methods of assessing a plausibility of a ranging measurement"
    img="/patent_uwb.webp" 
    desc="Algorithm for attack detection and plausibility assessment in UWB ranging. This invention improves the security of distance estimation against RF noise and relay attacks."
    url="#"
    badge="US Patent 63/431,772"
  />

  <div class="mt-10 p-6 bg-base-200 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-primary">
    <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Technical Portfolio Summary</h3>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2">
        <li><b>1 Patents</b> in High-Precision RTLS Localization.</li>
        <li><b>3 Patents</b> in Secure Entry & Radar Fusion.</li>
        <li><b>1 Patent</b> in UWB Physical Layer Security (ToF assessment).</li>
        <li><b>1 Patent</b> in Automotive Optimized Data Transfer.</li>
        <li><b>Patents in submission progress:</b> 1 patent.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm italic">Note: Specific patent titles and full documentation may be restricted due to NDA and pending status at the USPTO/EPO.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>